content.value: This suede trucker jacket is timeless investment piece (minus the investment). A modern take on the classic trucker features butter-soft yet durable Italian calf suede. Hand-finished details like smooth tobacco leather under-collar and midnight navy satin lining give just the right amount of personality.
Material: 100% Genuine Italian Calf Suede Leather
Lining: Midnight Navy 100% poly satin (fully lined)
Smooth contrast tobacco leather on underside of collar
Italian press stud fastening in a brushed nickel finish
5 pockets (two chest pockets, two main entry pockets, one interior pocket)

Leather sourced from a LWG (Leather Working Group) certified tannery; a non-profit aimed to promote sustainable business practices through low energy & water usage, waste management, and the elimination of restricted substances
Model is 6'1 and wearing the suede trucker jacket in a size Medium
Origin: Suede from Italy, Made in Turkey
Do not wash or dry clean. Professional leather dry clean only
